Package org.example

Class Iphone

java.lang.Object
org.example.Phone
org.example.Iphone
Direct Known Subclasses:
Iphone15ProMax, Iphone16Pro
public class Iphone extends Phone
The Iphone class represents a specific type of phone inheriting from the Phone class. It provides basic attributes such as battery life, color, material, and IMEI.

This class currently does not add additional functionality beyond the Phone class.
